{"id": "1374414025739468800", "channel_id": "1374414025739468800", "type": 0, "author_id": "452731110556696596", "author_name": "aurora3981", "author_bot": false, "content": "When gelot uses base chain (0/3), it gets slotted into the ultra bar as chain (1/3) but it behaves like chain (0/3). Same for subsequent chain, they get +1 before getting slotted into the ultra bar. The cap 3 still works tho so you won't see chain (4/3)\nHere's a video of fake chain (2/3), in reality it is (1/3).", "timestamp": "2025-05-20T15:50:39.114000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😲", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1374414026351841330", "filename": "Screen_Recording_20250520_232035_Morimens2.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 3704587, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1374414025739468800/1374414026351841330/Screen_Recording_20250520_232035_Morimens2.mp4?ex=69cbed4f&is=69ca9bcf&hm=5cc6f3c5d6db104623ea8dcc21a9dd30783935081f1a82b8978c5a44df4fcdc1&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1374414025739468800", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Gelot chain and Ultra bar UI bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
